{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"27cd03d3-b5dc-4083-8050-1bad0b9131a9","content":"`.testsettings` files are **no longer supported** in modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nHere's how your settings map:\n\n| `.testsettings` | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property | `<TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<DeploymentEnabled>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code Coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file like this:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_ug2tclgglZha4rWvHRjsEk","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-aff02374b9ee44659fa4cd75bc4a89d7/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <RunConfiguration>\n    <TestSessionTimeout>30000</TestSessionTimeout>\n  </RunConfiguration>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCollector, Microsoft.CodeCoverage, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-aff02374b9ee44659fa4cd75bc4a89d7/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"6818e40d-d058-4059-b6ed-bbb22280fa78","outputTokens":485,"requestId":"9C45:3B7ECE:1424F10:160EF39:69F86AEF"},"id":"40f8941a-dcd6-4985-8040-ac4725a71c4e","timestamp":"2026-05-04T09:46:31.354Z","parentId":"ff0d94b2-b8f3-449c-830e-510100aed495"}
